description: The remains of the galley lie shattered and dispersed throughout this room.  Splintered tables and benches lie in heaps throughout the room.  Wooden bowls and mugs, cracked and warped, can be seen amongst the junk in the room.  An arch leads to the hold to the east.

The remains of the galley lie shattered and dispersed throughout this room.  Splintered tables and the charred remains of benches lie in heaps throughout the room.  Wooden bowls and mugs, cracked and warped by heat, can be seen amongst the junk in the room.  An arch leads to the hold to the east.
title: [Vornavian Coast, Beached Hulk]
